        <div class="card-head">
          <h3>Awning vs Sliding vs Casement vs Tilt-and-Turn</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p>Consider the use of the windows because some types provide a sealed system like an awning window where heat and sound can't pass easily whereas a sliding window will have a small gap in the middle as it can't form a tight seal. When it's raining some types allow rain to come in more easily than others (e.g. awning vs sliding).</p>

